description: FlashZero Corp., a development stage company, through a licensing agreement with Two Dog Net, Inc., engages in marketing, selling, and administering an Internet service and online community for children. It offers The Children's Internet service that provides access to pre-selected and pre-approved educational and entertaining age appropriate Web pages, as well as email, homework help, games, news, and super portals to learning activities and educational resources in an online environment. The company was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Houston, Texas. FlashZero Corp. operats as a subsidiary of Shadrack Films Inc.
